  m_Name: FlyingSkullDialogue2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NpcDialogue
  npcName: Skull Spirit
  dialogueLines:
  - So... you made it through.
  - You have reached the first checkpoint. If you die, you will respawn here.
  - Few ever reach this place. Fewer still leave it.
  - Behind the castle, you will find a chest that contains a key. You need at least
    5 coins to open the chest.
  - Once you have retrieved the key, you must find 2 more hidden across the island.
  - You need to find all 3 keys to open the final chest and leave the island. Goodluck!
  - You have 2 minutes. Your time starts now.
